Package: BrainNetTest
Type: Package
Title: Hypothesis Testing for Brain Network Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Maximiliano", "Martino", email = "maxii.martino@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions to perform hypothesis testing on brain networks represented as graphs. It includes functionalities to compute central graphs, calculate distances using the Manhattan norm, and compute the test statistic T to determine if different populations of brain networks originate from the same distribution.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
